<div type="content">
<ab>Edler, lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr edel
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                            <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Stewdn<ex>er</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>priest<ex>er,</ex></expan> ein ewrs gesessen
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> sun zu Salburg, und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Tandorff<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen ewr edel
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricz<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Tandorff<ex>er</ex></expan> für uns besant und
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu red gesaczt
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Der hat uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz er der sache von seinselbs
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>zu
                            schike<ex>n</ex></expan> hab noch gehabt hab; im hab unser
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> der <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan>
                        von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g,</expan> vor <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zeite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>empfolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> gehabt, daz er von dem
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Stewdn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>einneme<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>empfahe<ex>n</ex></expan> sölt
                            ii<hi rend="sup">c</hi>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> von teyding <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        die <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan></add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Stewdn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>bescheh<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>. Also hab im der
                            <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> c und xxx <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; hett er im die
                            <expan>übrig<ex>en</ex></expan> lxx <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, er hett die auch
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> nucz
                        gekeret. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so spricht der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> auch wir
                        das dem <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>Fr<ex>icz</ex></expan>
<expan>Tandorff<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>völlikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Dewcht in, daz er
                            <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>ena</ex>nt</expan> icht zu <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        hett, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> von im <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um.</ex></expan>
</ab>
